The NFT will open up new opportunities for space enthusiasts to interact with astronauts like @Astro_Jose and others. There will be more access to launches from companies like @blueorigin Or @NASA. The NFT can help holders be at the forefront of the journey to the next frontier

Cool to see people like @Astro_Jose recognize the importance and utility of NFTs in real life applications. It's not a scam and not just about digital art. @spaceplusnft and @upliftaerospace are using NFTs to help expand access to space exploration to a wider community.

@WutzkeMegan @Astro_Jose @spaceplusnft There's a lot of misunderstanding and bad sentiment around NFTs mostly because of a few bad actors and the way that some people explain what an NFT is. But when done right and NFT is a game changer in terms of ownership rights and rewarding the artists, developers, and supporters
